\f0\fs24 \cf0 # MYAIRCRAFT.US \'97 INTEGRATIONS HUB + AUTO-REMINDERS INTELLIGENCE PROMPT\
\
You are extending the existing myaircraft.us product. Do NOT rebuild the app from scratch. Inspect the current codebase, preserve all working flows, and add a production-grade integrations layer for aircraft scheduling software plus an automatic reminders intelligence engine.\
\
## Primary mission\
Build a system where each customer account can connect external scheduling/ops software so that:\
\
1. aircraft can sync into myaircraft.us automatically\
2. aircraft tach / time / usage data can stay synchronized automatically\
3. reminders are generated and updated automatically from:\
   - aircraft registry data\
   - scheduling / dispatch / tach / flight activity feeds\
   - uploaded logbooks and scanned maintenance records\
   - FAA AD sources\
   - recurring compliance rules\
4. users do NOT need to manually enter every reminder\
5. reminders activate, update, and close automatically as more data arrives\
\
---\
\
## PRODUCT OBJECTIVE\
\
myaircraft.us should become the system of record for:\
- aircraft identity\
- aircraft documents\
- maintenance intelligence\
- reminders / due items / compliance tracking\
- AI search and evidence-backed Q&A\
\
Scheduling software should serve as a live operational signal source.\
Documents should serve as evidence and compliance source.\
FAA / authority data should serve as regulatory source.\
myaircraft.us should reconcile all of them.\
\
---\
\
## EXISTING PRODUCT REALITY TO RESPECT\
\
The product already has:\
- auth\
- org/customer context\
- aircraft pages\
- reminders foundations\
- document uploads\
- RAG foundations\
- FAA tail / aircraft lookup behavior\
- existing live app behavior\
\
Do NOT replace these with a parallel system.\
Extend the current product cleanly.\
